			<abstract>
				<p>Testimony of Ela Wowsi regarding the establishment of the Daugavpils Ghetto in July 1941, the liquidation actions in 1942, the mass
					executions during the final liquidation of the ghetto, and her imprisonment in the German concentration camps in Toruń and
					Stutthof.</p>
			</abstract>
